                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No record of the substance of this meeting has been found. The information given
                    here as to the meeting and the participants is taken from the Log, <hi
                        rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_553">p. 553</ref>, which states
                    that the discussions continued <pb facs="0705" n="611" xml:id="pg_611"/> until 4
                    p. m. On August 13, 1954, <persName corresp="#p_MHF1">Matthews</persName> wrote
                    of this meeting as follows: “I do not recall the subject but most such meetings
                    were to inform the President of the results of our morning Foreign Ministers
                    meeting and to prepare him for the afternoon agenda” (640.0029/8–1354).</p>
            </div>
        </body>
